question: Will the WHO declare a Public Health Emergency for H5N1 influenza by June 30?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if the World Health Organization (WHO) declares a Public Health Emergency of International Concern (PHEIC) for H5N1 influenza by June 30, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".  

The primary resolution source for this market will be official statements made by the WHO (e.g. statements released on their official website, https://www.who.int/), however a consensus of credible reporting will also be used.
